<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{% if title %}{{ title }} · {% endif %}{{ site.title }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta name="keywords" content="금융, 재테크, 증시, 투자 인사이트, 데일리 뉴스" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site.url }}" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{ site.url }}" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:site" content="@martin" />
  <style>
    :root {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background-color: #030513;
      color: #f1f3ff;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(19, 110, 210, 0.25), transparent 50%), #01030b;
    }
    .app-shell {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 16px 48px;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    }
    header .meta-tagline {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #9ddfff;
    }
    .layout-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(260px, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
    }
    section{ }
    .issue-card {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      background: rgba(6, 10, 27, 0.8);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }
    .issue-card h3 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .issue-card p { line-height: 1.7; }
    .issue-meta, .issue-source { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
    .tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-top:12px; }
    .tag { font-size:0.8rem; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .ad-slot {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      color: #98c6ff;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .ad-slot span { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    aside ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    footer { margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; justify-content:space-between; }
    .privacy-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .layout-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "NewsMediaOrganization",
      "name": "{{ site.title }}",
      "url": "{{ site.url }}",
      "description": "{{ site.description }}",
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "{{ site.title }}"
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-shell">
    <header>
      <div>
        <h1>{{ site.title }}</h1>
        <p class="meta-tagline">{{ site.description }}</p>
      </div>
      <nav aria-label="Quick links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}">홈</a>
        <a href="mailto:martin@example.com">문의</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">프라이버시</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="layout-grid">
      <div>
        {{ content | safe }}
      </div>
      <aside>
        <div class="ad-slot" aria-label="AdSense preview">
          <span>광고 슬롯 (Google AdSense 준비)</span>
          <strong>AdSense 300x250</strong>
          <p>위치: 사이드바 상단 · 목적: 수익화 및 뉴스레터 CTA</p>
        </div>
        <section aria-labelledby="why-updated">
          <h3 id="why-updated">Daily signal tracker</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>매일 오전 08:30(KST) 주요 글로벌 데이터 집계</li>
            <li>핵심 지표: 금리, 통화, 원자재, 기업 실적, 정책</li>
            <li>실시간 알림: Cloudflare build webhook → Telegram</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <div>
        © {{ today.now | year }} {{ site.author }} · Cloudflare Pages · Eleventy
      </div>
      <div class="privacy-links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
